title: WSB's Weekend Bite Week Ending April 15: Sell Tesla
author: Seeking Alpha

description: ETFs in the energy and cyber sectors, why Tesla is a sell after Musk's attempt to buy Twitter and whether we're in a risk on or risk off market. With Michelle Culver, VP Portfolio Strategist at Global X, and David Trainer, CEO of New Constructs.
